text: Marchais-en-Brie is a former commune. It is found in the region Hauts-de- France in the Aisne department in the north of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune Dhuys-et-Morin-en-Brie.Arrêté préfectoral 10 September 2015 ==References== Category:Former communes in Aisne
title: Marchais-en-Brie
